tanhope and Mr. Craggs, both &s;ecretaries of &s;tate. &sect; <HI>XXXI.</HI> The e&s;tates of the directors of the South-&s;ea company are confi&s;cated. &sect; <HI>XXXII.</HI> Proceedings of the commons with re&s;pect to the &s;tock of the South-&s;ea com|pany.</P>
