ect; <HI>XXXII.</HI> Debate in the hou&s;e of lords upon the approaching rupture with the emperor and Spain. &sect; <HI>XXXIII.</HI> Memorial of Mr. Palms the Imperial re&s;ident at London. &sect; <HI>XXXIV.</HI> Conventions with Sweden and He&s;&s;e-Ca&s;&s;el. &sect; <HI>XXXV.</HI> Vote of credit. &sect; <HI>XXXVI.</HI> Siege of Gibraltar by the Spaniards. &sect; <HI>XXXVII.</HI> Preliminaries of peace. &sect; <HI>XXXVIII.</HI> Death and character of George <HI>I.</HI> king of Great-Britain.</P>
